        "**Late 2000s to Early 2010s:**\n",
        "The period shows some alignment between rising inflation in India and a weakening INR, which indicates that inflation could be contributing to exchange rate movements.\n",
        "\n",
        "**2015 Onwards:**\n",
        "The exchange rate continues to rise, while both India’s and the United States’ inflation rates remain relatively low."
